{"tid":2094584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"邵家臻: 輕度智障清潔工早前被判囚8個月 警方將就另案加控三條罪名","createTime":"2020-07-04T18:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:26:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"682e81113a5c9e51a8ef8c6299bb28a352da197e","tid":2094584,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:09:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/photos/a.200856493433676/1413840902135223/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbottleshiukachun%2Fphotos%2Fa.200856493433676%2F1413840902135223%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=fe2229a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/photos/a.200856493433676/1413840902135223/</a><br />\n<br />\n有好消息，亦有壞消息，都是關於發仔的。之前說發仔被警暴，門牙被打掉，很多有心人願意出錢出力為發仔治療。昨天發生已經配好牙套，算是補回幾隻門牙。我們亦已經跟他食期待已久的日式拉麵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">然而，今日下午發仔就在旺角警署被加控三條罪名：<br />\n1，非法集結<br />\n2，蒙面<br />\n3，攻擊性武器<br />\n在7月14日上午要上庭應訊。對一個弱智人士都落得如此重手，就算早對政府沒有期望，也感到齒冷。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dfbb1e4a03b3173ca5717d1efad7fe79a1e1dd68","tid":2094584,"uid":124180,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚嘢世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e92b424b24be6a8ec5cbbc7800aa24c0db80be7","tid":2094584,"uid":273157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"想問畫家呢家點？"},{"pid":"c7a66918ea5ee0650a14d76255d9e462dec99452","tid":2094584,"uid":231089,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:12:04.000Z","msg":"政府真係好撚垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n屌 天生mentally impaired本身應該就要多d關心佢地 痴撚線 死黑警仲要整爆人地門牙 <br />\n<br />\n求神拜佛律師一定要幫手足打甩佢 痴撚線世界"},{"p